headline: S&P 500 Earnings This Week: FOMC Decision, Mega-Cap Tech Earnings, And December PCE On Friday
summary: Tesla, Meta and Microsoft report after the closing bell on Jan. 29; Apple, Intel and Visa report on Jan. 30. December PCE and Core PCE are due on Jan. 31; consensus expects +0.2% Core PCE.
